  "transliteration": "Wa yusabbiḥur-ra‘du biḥamdihī wal-malā'ikatu min khīfatih(ī), wa yursiluṣ-ṣawā‘iqa fa yuṣību bihā may yasyā'u wa hum yujālidilūna fillāh(i), wa huwa syadīdul-miḥāl(i)."
